lastCommitMessage: refactor: enhance image processing logic in seller product page
- Improved the handling of existing and newly uploaded images by ensuring that deleted images are excluded from the final list.
- Added detailed logging for better tracking of image processing steps, including the retention of file IDs for existing images and the addition of newly uploaded images.
- Streamlined the logic for uploading new web images and handling upload failures, enhancing overall user feedback.
These changes aim to improve the image management experience on the seller product page and enhance code clarity.
